<footer class="footer">
  <div class="footer-inner">

    <div class="footer-brand">
      <span class="logo">Tecni<em>Ya</em></span>
      <p>Conectando hogares con técnicos de confianza.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer-col">
      <p class="footer-col-title">Síguenos</p>
      <div class="footer-socials">
        <a href="https://www.instagram.com/tecni_ya_oficial?igsh=ZXZzNjhkbDdxandt" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="social-btn" aria-label="TikTok">
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M19.59 6.69a4.83 4.83 0 01-3.77-4.25V2h-3.45v13.67a2.89 2.89 0 01-2.88 2.5 2.89 2.89 0 01-2.89-2.89 2.89 2.89 0 012.89-2.89c.28 0 .54.04.79.1V9.01a6.33 6.33 0 00-.79-.05 6.34 6.34 0 00-6.34 6.34 6.34 6.34 0 006.34 6.34 6.34 6.34 0 006.33-6.34V8.97a8.16 8.16 0 004.77 1.52V7.04a4.85 4.85 0 01-1-.35z"/>
          </svg>
          TikTok
        </a>
        
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer-col">
      <p class="footer-col-title">¿Problemas o dudas?</p>
      <p class="footer-contact-desc">Nuestro equipo de atención al cliente está disponible para ayudarte.</p>
      <a
        href="https://wa.me/51994839050?text=Hola%20TecniYa%2C%20tengo%20una%20consulta"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener"
        class="whatsapp-btn"
        aria-label="Contactar por WhatsApp"
        onclick="gtag('event','click_whatsapp')"
        >
        <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51-.173-.008-.371-.01-.57-.01-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372-.272.297-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 0 1.462 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347m-5.421 7.403h-.004a9.87 9.87 0 01-5.031-1.378l-.361-.214-3.741.982.998-3.648-.235-.374a9.86 9.86 0 01-1.51-5.26c.001-5.45 4.436-9.884 9.888-9.884 2.64 0 5.122 1.03 6.988 2.898a9.825 9.825 0 012.893 6.994c-.003 5.45-4.437 9.884-9.885 9.884m8.413-18.297A11.815 11.815 0 0012.05 0C5.495 0 .16 5.335.157 11.892c0 2.096.547 4.142 1.588 5.945L.057 24l6.305-1.654a11.882 11.882 0 005.683 1.448h.005c6.554 0 11.89-5.335 11.893-11.893a11.821 11.821 0 00-3.48-8.413z"/>
        </svg>
        Escríbenos por WhatsApp
      </a>
    </div>

  </div>

  <div class="footer-bottom center">
    <p>© 2025 TecniYa. Todos los derechos reservados.</p>
    
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
  .footer {
    border-top: 0.5px solid var(--border);
    padding: 3.5rem 2rem 2rem;
    background: var(--bg2);
  }

  .footer-inner {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto 2.5rem;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.4fr 1fr 1.4fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .logo {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--white);
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }
  .logo em { font-style: normal; color: var(--orange); }

  .footer-brand p {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .footer-col-title {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .footer-socials {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.6rem;
  }

  .social-btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-decoration: none;
    padding: 8px 14px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border: 0.5px solid var(--border);
    background: var(--bg3);
    transition: color 0.2s, border-color 0.2s, background 0.2s;
    width: fit-content;
  }
  .social-btn:hover {
    color: var(--white);
    border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
  }

  .footer-contact-desc {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .whatsapp-btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    background: #25D366;
    color: #fff;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 11px 20px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    transition: opacity 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
  }
  .whatsapp-btn:hover {
    opacity: 0.88;
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }

  .footer-bottom {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    border-top: 0.5px solid var(--border);
    padding-top: 1.5rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .footer-bottom p {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: rgba(136,146,164,0.5);
  }

  .back-top {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-decoration: none;
    padding: 6px 14px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    border: 0.5px solid var(--border);
    transition: color 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
  }
  .back-top:hover {
    color: var(--white);
    border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .footer-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2rem; }
    .footer-bottom { justify-content: center; text-align: center; }
  }
</style>